<item>
            <title>[LU-12294] Memory leak after recovery packet processing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12294</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the driver stops, resources for recovery packets will be released.&lt;br/&gt;
But, If recovery process is working at this time, resources are not released.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We correct to wait for recovery packets to be unlinked.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
